urban morphology 中文翻譯
中文翻譯手機版城市形態學urban:    adj. 1.城市的，在城市裡的，住在城市中的，城市居民 ...morphology:    n. 【生、地】形態學；【語法】詞法；詞態學；【生物學】 ...morphology:    n. 【生、地】形態學；【語法】詞法；詞態學；【生物學】組織,形態。 n. -gist  形態學家。 urban:    adj. 1.城市的，在城市裡的，住在城市中的，城市居民的。 2.習慣於[喜愛]城市生活的。  the urban population 城市人口 ...accordant morphology:    平齊地貌age morphology:    年齡形態學animal morphology:    動物形態學bacterial morphology:    細菌形態學blood morphology:    血液形態學cell morphology:    泡孔形態; 細胞形態學cellular morphology:    細胞形態學channel morphology:    河床地貌; 河床形態chromosome morphology:    染色體形態學coastal morphology:    海岸形態學colonial morphology:    菌落形態學comparative morphology:    比較刑態學; 比較形態學concordant morphology:    平齊地貌constructional morphology:    構造形態學crack morphology:    裂紋形貌cryst morphology:    晶體形態學crystal morphology:    晶體結構; 晶體形態學; 形態結晶學crystalline morphology:    結晶形態學crystallization morphology:    結晶形態學cultural morphology:    文化形態delta morphology:    三角洲形態
例句與用法The development of shophouses in urban morphology in asian cities亞洲城市的騎樓發展Spatial - temporal evolution of urban morphology and land use structure in hangzhou杭州城市形態和土地利用結構的時空演化Deshong , m . " housing typology and urban morphology : london and paris . " 1990居住類型學與都市形態學：倫敦與巴黎， 1990 Spatial visibility analysis is a novel method in urban morphology and spatial configuration , which is an important tool in space syntax摘要空間可視分析是空間句法的重要依據，是進行城市空間形態分析的新方法。 Space syntax analysis is on important tool of urban morphology quantification study , and integration is the most effective parameter which is used usually in space syntax analysis摘要空間句法分析是城市形態量化研究的重要工縣、集成度是空間句法分析中最有效最常用的參數。 The rate and magnitude of urbanization in comparison to the capacity of the land to absorb the expansion can have bearing on the resultant urban morphology and hence the availability of plantable spaces隨著急劇的都市發展，城市的發展速度規模和潛在土地拓展空間對都市面貌及綠化區構成重大影向。完善的現代都市計劃總會預留空間作種植之用。 After analyzing urumqi historical evolution and development processes of the urban morphology , spatial characters , and mechanisms and factors , the paper brings out some suggestion of city plan and construction , and propose the conceiving plan of the urban developing orientation in the future32 ，分佈在起伏度指數7上的土地所占比重最大，占14 54 。全研究區地形分佈表現出低、中、高三段式空間分佈結構。 This article analyzes the space syntax of xiamen urban morphology development and two master plans , summarizes the characteristics of xiamen urban morphology , and comes up with another choice of urban structure , for bath xiamen island and the whole xiamen city該文從本島和全市域兩個空間層次，分別對廈門城市形態發展過程和兩次總體規劃成果進行空間句法分析、總結廈門城市形態發展的特征，並提出其城市結構的另一種選擇。 Part one is to establish a framework of " compact city " theory through the research of urban morphology , analyzing the logical connection between concentration and decentralization of urban morphology , compact urban morphology and the principles and goals of " compact city "理論研究部分通過對城市形態、集中與分散的邏輯關系、個體城市緊湊形態及“緊湊城市”涵蓋內容的分析，建立“緊湊城市”的理論框架，明確“緊湊城市”的基本原則和根本目標。 At present in china , there are gaps between the master planning and the detail planning during the space figuration process of urban design . therefore , in order to make up these shortcomings on the neglecting of urban morphology , it is important to implement new ideas in the process of urban planning , thus it will benefit a lot of cities目前，我國城市總體規劃與詳細規劃在城市整體空間形態控制上存在一定程度的脫節現象，將城市設計思想貫穿到城市總體規劃過程中，彌補總體規劃對城市空間形態考慮不足的現象，解決大面積的城市形象問題有重要意義。 用"urban morphology"造句  
百科解釋Urban morphology is the study of the form of human settlements and the process of their formation and transformation. The study seeks to understand the spatial structure and character of a metropolitan area, city, town or village by examining the patterns of its component parts and the process of its development.詳細百科解釋


